title: my contacts app shows more contact than i have?
content:
I selected to show only exchange contacts in contacts app.
I have 1152 person in windows outlook 2016 software's contacts part.
But google shows me 1754 contacts and many of them without phone number etc.
How i can get rid of these unnecessary contacts?
category: Contacts, Calls, Voicemail, Google Pixel 3 XL
